HEADWORD: Genitocrural
<hw>Gen`i*to*cru"ral</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Genit</ets>al + <ets>crural</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to the genital organs and the thigh; -- applied
especially to one of the lumbar nerves.</def>⟦br⟧
